<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ARTEM DENISOV — СИСТЕМА РОСТА 2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #0a0a0a;
    --white: #f0ede6;
    --accent: #e8d44d;
    --red: #e84d4d;
    --blue: #4d8fe8;
    --green: #4de87a;
    --gray: #2a2a2a;
    --gray2: #1a1a1a;
    --muted: #666;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    padding: 40px 40px 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: end;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .header-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .header-name span { color: var(--accent); }

  .header-meta {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .header-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* COUNTDOWN */
  .countdown-bar {
    background: var(--gray2);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .countdown-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .countdown-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .countdown-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .countdown-divider { color: #333; font-size: 24px; }

  /* PROGRESS BAR */
  .progress-bar-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .progress-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .progress-track {
    height: 4px;
    background: #333;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }

  /* MAIN GRID */
  .main {
    padding: 32px 40px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 16px; }
    .header { padding: 24px 16px 16px; }
    .countdown-bar { padding: 12px 16px; gap: 20px; }
  }

  /* BLOCK */
  .block {
    background: var(--gray2);
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .block:hover { border-color: #333; }

  .block-wide {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .block-full {
    grid-column: span 3;
  }

  .block-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    right: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .block-tag {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .block-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* STATUS PILLS */
  .status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .status-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .status.active { background: rgba(78,232,122,0.1); color: var(--green); }
  .status.active .status-dot { background: var(--green); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  .status.pending { background: rgba(232,212,77,0.1); color: var(--accent); }
  .status.pending .status-dot { background: var(--accent); }
  .status.critical { background: rgba(232,77,77,0.1); color: var(--red); }
  .status.critical .status-dot { background: var(--red); }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  /* CHECKLIST */
  .checklist { list-style: none; }

  .checklist li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .checklist li:hover { padding-left: 4px; }

  .check-box {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #444;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .check-box.done {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .check-box.done::after {
    content: '✓';
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--black);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .check-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #ccc;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .check-text.done {
    color: #555;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .check-meta {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* METRICS */
  .metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .metric {
    background: #111;
    padding: 14px;
    border: 1px solid #222;
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .metric-now {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .metric-target {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .metric-bar {
    height: 2px;
    background: #333;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .metric-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--green));
  }

  /* ROADMAP */
  .roadmap { margin-top: 4px; }

  .roadmap-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .roadmap-month {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-top: 12px;
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .roadmap-content {
    background: #111;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-left: 2px solid #333;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .roadmap-content.now { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .roadmap-content.soon { border-color: #333; }
  .roadmap-content.later { border-color: #1e1e1e; opacity: 0.7; }

  .roadmap-focus {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .roadmap-detail {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* RESOURCES */
  .resources { margin-top: 4px; }

  .resource-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
  }

  .resource-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .resource-icon {
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .resource-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .resource-text strong {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .resource-cat {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* WEEKLY RHYTHM */
  .week-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
    gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .day-col { }

  .day-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .day-item {
    background: #111;
    padding: 6px 4px;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: #777;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .day-item.sport { border-color: var(--blue); color: #7ab3e8; }
  .day-item.mental { border-color: var(--green); color: #7ae89a; }
  .day-item.work { border-color: var(--accent); color: #e8d07a; }
  .day-item.off { opacity: 0.3; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    padding: 24px 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: gap;
  }

  .footer-text {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #333;
  }

  .footer-motto {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #222;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
  }

  /* SCORE */
  .score-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .score-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 16px 8px;
    background: #111;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .score-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

  .score-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
    display: block;
  }

  .score-area {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 4px;
    display: block;
  }

  .score-edit {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .score-btn {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background: #222;
    border: none;
    color: var(--white);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .score-btn:hover { background: var(--accent); color: var(--black); }

  /* JOURNAL */
  .journal-entry {
    background: #111;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-left: 2px solid #333;
  }

  .journal-date {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .journal-input {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    width: 100%;
    resize: none;
    outline: none;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .journal-input::placeholder { color: #444; }

  .add-entry-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 100%;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .add-entry-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }

  /* TABS */
  .tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
  }

  .tab {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .tab.active {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .tab-content { display: none; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }

  /* SECTION DIVIDER */
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    padding: 24px 40px 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid #111;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .block-wide, .block-full { grid-column: span 1; }
    .score-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .week-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
    .metrics { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .section-label { padding: 16px 16px 8px; }
    .footer { padding: 16px; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div>
    <div class="header-name">АРТЁМ <span>ДЕНИСОВ</span></div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px">
      <span class="header-tag">СИСТЕМА РОСТА 2026–2027</span>
      <span class="header-tag" style="background:#1a1a1a;color:#666">VP READY</span>
      <span class="header-tag" style="background:#1a1a1a;color:#666">ТРИАТЛОН · ОЛИМПИК</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-meta">
    38 лет · 186 см · 82 кг<br>
    Директор B2C · 1500+ команда<br>
    <span id="today-date"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- COUNTDOWN -->
<div class="countdown-bar">
  <div class="countdown-item">
    <div class="countdown-num" id="days-to-race">—</div>
    <div class="countdown-label">дней до<br>триатлона</div>
  </div>
  <div class="countdown-divider">/</div>
  <div class="countdown-item">
    <div class="countdown-num" id="days-year">—</div>
    <div class="countdown-label">дней<br>в карте</div>
  </div>
  <div class="countdown-divider">/</div>
  <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
    <div class="progress-label">
      <span>ПРОГРЕСС ГОДА</span>
      <span id="year-pct">—%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-track">
      <div class="progress-fill" id="year-fill" style="width:0%"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SCORE SECTION -->
<div class="section-label">// ЕЖЕНЕДЕЛЬНЫЙ ПУЛЬС — обновляй каждое воскресенье</div>
<div style="padding: 0 40px 0; background: var(--gray2); border-bottom: 1px solid #111;">
  <div style="padding: 20px 0;">
    <div class="score-grid">
      <div class="score-item" id="score-career">
        <span class="score-num" id="v-career">7</span>
        <span class="score-area">Карьера</span>
        <div class="score-edit">
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('career',-1)">−</button>
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('career',1)">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item" id="score-sport">
        <span class="score-num" id="v-sport">8</span>
        <span class="score-area">Спорт</span>
        <div class="score-edit">
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('sport',-1)">−</button>
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('sport',1)">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item" id="score-mental">
        <span class="score-num" id="v-mental">6</span>
        <span class="score-area">Ментал</span>
        <div class="score-edit">
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('mental',-1)">−</button>
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('mental',1)">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item" id="score-family">
        <span class="score-num" id="v-family">5</span>
        <span class="score-area">Семья</span>
        <div class="score-edit">
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('family',-1)">−</button>
          <button class="score-btn" onclick="changeScore('family',1)">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item" style="border-color: var(--accent);">
        <span class="score-num" id="v-total" style="color:var(--accent)">—</span>
        <span class="score-area" style="color:var(--accent)">Итого/40</span>
        <div style="height:28px"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN BLOCKS -->
<div class="section-label">// АКТИВНЫЕ ТРЕКИ</div>
<div class="main">

  <!-- SPORT -->
  <div class="block">
    <div class="block-num">01</div>
    <div class="block-tag">// спорт</div>
    <div class="block-title" style="color:var(--blue)">ТРИАТЛОН<br>ОЛИМПИК</div>
    <div class="status active"><div class="status-dot"></div>АКТИВНО · 21 ИЮНЯ</div>

    <div class="metrics">
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Плавание/100м</div>
        <div class="metric-now">1:36</div>
        <div class="metric-target">→ цель 1:20</div>
        <div class="metric-bar"><div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width:65%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Велосипед 40км</div>
        <div class="metric-now">1:02</div>
        <div class="metric-target">→ цель 1:00</div>
        <div class="metric-bar"><div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width:85%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Бег темп/км</div>
        <div class="metric-now">4:15</div>
        <div class="metric-target">→ цель 4:00 ⚠️</div>
        <div class="metric-bar"><div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Тренировок/нед</div>
        <div class="metric-now">5-6</div>
        <div class="metric-target">→ держать</div>
        <div class="metric-bar"><div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width:90%"></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:16px">
      <div class="block-tag" style="margin-bottom:8px">// фокус до старта</div>
      <ul class="checklist" id="sport-list">
        <li onclick="toggle(this)">
          <div class="check-box"></div>
          <div><div class="check-text">Интервалы бег: 6×1км на 3:55 — 2×/неделю</div><div class="check-meta">ГЛАВНЫЙ ПРИОРИТЕТ</div></div>
        </li>
        <li onclick="toggle(this)">
          <div class="check-box"></div>
          <div><div class="check-text">Кирпичная тренировка вело→бег — 1×/неделю</div><div class="check-meta">ПЕРЕХОДНАЯ ЗОНА</div></div>
        </li>
        <li onclick="toggle(this)">
          <div class="check-box"></div>
          <div><div class="check-text">Отработать T1/T2 зоны — 3-4 раза физически</div><div class="check-meta">СЭКОНОМИШЬ 2-3 МИНУТЫ</div></div>
        </li>
        <li onclick="toggle(this)">
          <div class="check-box"></div>
          <div><div class="check-text">Tapering: -30% объём за 2 недели до старта</div><div class="check-meta">С 7 ИЮНЯ</div></div>
        </li>
        <li onclick="toggle(this)">
          <div class="check-box"></div>
          <div><div class="check-text">Выбрать следующий старт — сентябрь/октябрь</div><div class="check-meta">ПОСЛЕ 21 ИЮНЯ</div></div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CAREER -->
  <div class="block">
    <div class="block-num">02</div>
    <div class="block-tag">// карьера</div>
    <div class="block-title" style="color:var(--accent)">VP/C-LEVEL<br>ПЕРЕХОД</div>
    <div class="status pending"><div class="status-dot"></div>СТАРТ — ИЮЛЬ 2026</div>

    <ul class="checklist">
      <li onclick="toggle(this)">
        <div class="check-box"></div>
        <div><div class="check-text">Переписать резюме: продажа → не отчёт</div><div class="check-meta">МАЙ · ФАЗА УПАКОВКИ</div></div>
